      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i've been reading a lot about how the demographics in the US are shifting pretty fast. from a political science perspective, how do you think the increasing population of Hispanic and Latino voters is going to affect the long-term stability of western democratic institutions? like, will it change the fundamental way these systems function?",
